Riso Banking System

Documentation
-------------

The full documentation is at https://riso-banking.readthedocs.io.

Quickstart
----------

Install Riso Banking System::

    pip install riso-banking

Add it to your `INSTALLED_APPS`:

.. code-block:: python

    INSTALLED_APPS = (
        ...
        'riso_banking.apps.RisoBankingConfig',
        ...
    )

Add Riso Banking System's URL patterns:

.. code-block:: python

    from riso_banking import urls as riso_banking_urls


    urlpatterns = [
        ...
        url(r'^', include(riso_banking_urls)),
        ...
    ]
